      <hc>We're days away from posting a Content Guide for food-related events here, to give you some guidance on planning your event.</hc></br>
      <hc>We'll also post the guide at the <a href="http://osmlab.github.io/teachosm/en/">TeachOSM site</a> (<i>under development</i>)
       so you can use it for future lesson plans, project ideas<br/>
        or for your classroom, seminar, club.
